metadata.description:
In 2011, Steve Jobs have shared an important insight that I remembered for a long time:

“Technology alone is not enough. It’s technology married with the liberal arts, married with the humanities, that yields the results that makes our hearts sing.”

We are now entering a brand new era where technology and liberal arts are fusing and collapsing on each other.
